<tr>
<td>Basic Required Courses</td>
<td>Calculus, Physics, Statics, Structural Analysis</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Field Courses</td>
<td>Soil Mechanics, Fluid Mechanics, Transportation Engineering</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Elective Specializations</td>
<td>Smart Infrastructure, Green Building Design, BIM</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to see the curriculum in detail, you can also take a look at <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-universitesi-egitim-ucretleri/" data-type="post" data-id="3013">Özyeğin University Tuition Fees and Payment Options</a>. On this page you can find clear information about both costs and payment plans.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-quality-of-education-for-international-students-at-ozyegin">The Quality of Education for International Students at Ozyegin</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="english-education-and-academic-staff">English Education and Academic Staff</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University offers a great advantage for international students with its 100% English medium of instruction. This is especially valuable for students who plan to pursue a career outside Turkey after graduation. The academic staff at the university consists of faculty members with international experience, publications and field experience. They work with a system that blends theoretical knowledge with practice.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university also offers orientation programs for foreign students, Turkish language support courses and special counseling services. So you are not alone from the moment you step on campus.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="research-projects-laboratories-and-internship-opportunities">Research Projects, Laboratories and Internship Opportunities</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Department of Civil Engineering has advanced laboratories in the fields of soils, building materials, structural mechanics and transportation. Here, students have the chance to apply their theoretical knowledge one-on-one. Being involved in scientific projects while still a student is one of the most important steps to strengthen your CV.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition, thanks to collaborations with Turkey&#8217;s leading construction companies, students have professional internship opportunities in their 3rd and 4th years. This makes the transition to work after graduation much easier.</p>


<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="studying-civil-engineering-at-ozyegin-university">Studying Civil Engineering at Ozyegin University</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="specialization-with-certificate-programs">Specialization with Certificate Programs</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University blends civil engineering not only with traditional methods but also with the technologies of the future. There are special certificate programs that offer students the opportunity to specialize in <strong>&#8220;Climate Change and Sustainability&#8221;</strong> or <strong>&#8220;Digitalization and Artificial Intelligence&#8221;</strong>. These certificates make a difference in job applications both locally and internationally.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="career-opportunities-in-turkey-and-abroad-after-graduation">Career Opportunities in Turkey and Abroad After Graduation</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As a civil engineer, you can work on major projects in Turkey, but you can also work in Europe or the Middle East. Özyeğin University graduates go into business life in consulting firms, public institutions, research centers or by establishing their own ventures.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition to being engineers, the Department of Civil Engineering equips students to be researchers, project managers or academicians.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="areas-where-graduates-can-go">Areas where graduates can go</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Building and construction companies (domestic/foreign)</li>



<li>Project consulting companies</li>



<li>Infrastructure and transportation projects</li>



<li>Academic career and research centers</li>



<li>Sustainable building and green energy projects</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="life-in-istanbul-ozyegin-campus-and-student-life">Life in Istanbul: Özyeğin Campus and Student Life</h3>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="cost-of-living-and-accommodation-for-international-students">Cost-of-living and Accommodation for International Students</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Living in a large and vibrant city like Istanbul provides international students with cultural diversity and social experience. Özyeğin University campus is located in an area close to the city center but surrounded by nature.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">University dormitories are very attractive for students with their safe and comfortable structure. In addition, the campus has a gymnasium, library, student clubs and many areas for social activities.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="location-and-social-facilities-of-the-campus">Location and Social Facilities of the Campus</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin&#8217;s campus stands out with its modern architecture in the east of Istanbul. Students can take nature walks between classes and spend time with their friends in social areas. In addition, the entrepreneurship center on campus provides students with support in project development.</p>


<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="you-can-be-the-civil-engineer-of-the-future">You Can Be the Civil Engineer of the Future!</h3>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="application-process-and-tips">Application Process and Tips</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are excited about Özyeğin University Civil Engineering, it is important to prepare for the application process in advance. It helps to research the necessary documents, English proficiency requirements and the visa process in advance. The university&#8217;s international office is very helpful in this regard.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>What documents should I upload when registering? </strong><br>Don&#8217;t worry, the university has made this process as transparent as possible for you. You can find a list of all required documents <a href="https://www.ozyegin.edu.tr/tr/ogrenci-hizmetleri/universiteye-kayitlar/yurt-disindan-ogrenci-ydo-kontenjanindan-kabul-alan-0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>. Uploading complete documents ensures fast processing of the application.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There is also good news for those planning to pursue a master&#8217;s degree: <br><strong>In engineering fields such as <strong>Industrial, Mechanical, Electrical-Electronics, Civil, Computer Engineering and Architecture</strong>, as well as programs with thesis such as <strong>Physics, Mathematics, Artificial Intelligence and Data Science</strong>, foreign students are exempt from the <strong>Graduate Education Entrance Exam</strong>. However, if you have exam results such as GRE, ALES, etc., presenting them can give you an additional advantage.</strong></p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-07-23T10:21:42Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:52:32Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ozyegin-university-civil-engineerin.webp","alt":"Foreign students conducting an experiment in the civil engineering laboratory at Ozyegin University campus.","title":"ozyegin-university-civil-engineerin"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'ozyegin-construction-engineering';
