sting","name":"Özyeğin University Civil Engineering 2025 - RoadtoStudy","articleSection":"University and Programs","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-construction-engineering/#schema-11502","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-construction-engineering/#webpage"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-construction-engineering/#webpage"}},{"@type":"VideoObject","name":"Özyeğin University Civil Engineering 2025 - RoadtoStudy","description":"Enjoy the videos and music you love, upload original content, and share it all with friends, family, and the world on YouTube.","uploadDate":"2025-07-23T13:21:42+03:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ozyegin-university-civil-engineerin.webp","embedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/viQE4dMIqBw","isFamilyFriendly":"True","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-construction-engineering/#schema-11503","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-construction-engineering/#webpage"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-construction-engineering/#webpage"}}]}]}'), '$.content_html', '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For international students interested in studying engineering in Turkey, Özyeğin University stands out with its English-language programs, academic staff and dynamic campus life in Istanbul. In particular, the <strong>Civil Engineering Program</strong>, with its modern infrastructure, offers not only a diploma but also a strong foundation for an international career.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="Bir Bölüm Üç Açı - İnşaat Mühendisliği Mezun &amp; Öğrenci" width="720" height="405" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/viQE4dMIqBw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>


<div style="height:21px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ozyegin-university-faculty-of-engineering">Ozyegin University Faculty of Engineering</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University Faculty of Engineering is known for its interdisciplinary approach and applied education model. The Civil Engineering department within the faculty offers education not only at undergraduate but also at master&#8217;s and doctoral level, opening the door to a research-based career. If you want to get more information about <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-muhendislik-fakultesi/" data-type="post" data-id="3048">Özyeğin University Faculty of Engineering</a>, you can take a detailed look.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-much-does-civil-engineering-tuition-cost-2025-2026">How Much Does Civil Engineering Tuition Cost? 2025-2026</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many private universities in Turkey update their tuition fees every year. Özyeğin University has set the <strong>annual tuition fee for the <strong>Faculty of Engineering</strong> at 22,000 USD</strong> as of 2026. This fee is the standard list for non-scholarship (i.e. 0% scholarship) students.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Below, you can see the current fee and scholarship status of Özyeğin University Faculty of Engineering for 2025-2026 by department:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Department</th>
<th>Cost of Study (USD/Year)</th>
<th>Language of Study</th>
<th>Scholarship Opportunities</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>Civil Engineering</strong></td>
<td>$22,000</td>
<td>English</td>
<td>Full / 50% / Paid</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These fees are annual and do not remain fixed throughout the study period; the university may update them by 10-20% each year. However, the scholarship rate indicated at the time of admission remains fixed for the entire duration of the student&#8217;s studies.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-much-do-you-pay-with-scholarships">How much do you pay with scholarships?</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Full Scholarship</strong>: $0 (Free)</li>



<li><strong>50% Scholarship</strong>: $11,000</li>



<li><strong>Paid</strong> (without scholarship): $22,000</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-civil-engineering-what-is-its-purpose">What is Civil Engineering, What is its Purpose?</h2>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="this-occupation-is-not-limited-to-buildings">This Occupation is Not Limited to Buildings</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">While only buildings come to mind when we think of civil engineering, this field is actually divided into many sub-disciplines such as water structures, transportation systems, environmental engineering and earth sciences. Therefore, this program provides not only engineering but also a broad vision of design, environmental awareness and sustainability.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="a-globally-valid-occupation">A Globally Valid Occupation</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Civil engineering is a profession that is in global demand and recognized in <strong>every country</strong>. Özyeğin University aims to provide its students with the technical equipment and cultural understanding to work in different geographies. When you graduate, you can find a job not only in Turkey but also in many regions from Europe to the Gulf countries.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-courses-will-you-take-in-the-civil-engineering-program">What Courses Will You Take in the Civil Engineering Program?</h2>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="basic-courses-and-technical-competencies">Basic Courses and Technical Competencies</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Basic Lessons Learned in the Early Years:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Mathematics (Calculus I-II)</li>



<li>Physics (Mechanics, Electricity &amp; Magnetism)</li>



<li>Engineering Drawing and Technical Drawing</li>



<li>Computer Aided Design (CAD)</li>



<li>Materials Science</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Field Courses Taken in Upper Grades:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Structure Statics and Strength</li>



<li>Geotechnical Engineering</li>



<li>Hydraulics and Water Resources</li>



<li>Building Materials</li>



<li>Transport Engineering</li>



<li>Construction Management and Project Planning</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>English Education Advantage:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Ease of access to international resources</li>



<li>Knowledge of global engineering terminology</li>



<li>Advantage in international graduate applications</li>
</ul>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="specialization-areas-sustainability-and-digitalization">Specialization Areas: Sustainability and Digitalization</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In the final years of the program, students have the opportunity to specialize according to their interests. Two main areas of specialization are offered:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Climate Change and Sustainability</strong></li>



<li><strong>Digitalization and Artificial Intelligence in Civil Engineering</strong></li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This way, competencies are gained to produce solutions not only for today&#8217;s problems but also for the problems of the future.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="sample-table-of-compulsory-and-elective-courses">Sample Table of Compulsory and Elective Courses</h4>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Course Category</th>
<th>Course Examples</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Basic Required Courses</td>
<td>Calculus, Physics, Statics, Structural Analysis</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Field Courses</td>
<td>Soil Mechanics, Fluid Mechanics, Transportation Engineering</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Elective Specializations</td>
<td>Smart Infrastructure, Green Building Design, BIM</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to see the curriculum in detail, you can also take a look at <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-universitesi-egitim-ucretleri/" data-type="post" data-id="3013">Özyeğin University Tuition Fees and Payment Options</a>. On this page you can find clear information about both costs and payment plans.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-quality-of-education-for-international-students-at-ozyegin">The Quality of Education for International Students at Ozyegin</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="english-education-and-academic-staff">English Education and Academic Staff</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University offers a great advantage for international students with its 100% English medium of instruction. This is especially valuable for students who plan to pursue a career outside Turkey after graduation. The academic staff at the university consists of faculty members with international experience, publications and field experience. They work with a system that blends theoretical knowledge with practice.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university also offers orientation programs for foreign students, Turkish language support courses and special counseling services. So you are not alone from the moment you step on campus.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="research-projects-laboratories-and-internship-opportunities">Research Projects, Laboratories and Internship Opportunities</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Department of Civil Engineering has advanced laboratories in the fields of soils, building materials, structural mechanics and transportation. Here, students have the chance to apply their theoretical knowledge one-on-one. Being involved in scientific projects while still a student is one of the most important steps to strengthen your CV.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition, thanks to collaborations with Turkey&#8217;s leading construction companies, students have professional internship opportunities in their 3rd and 4th years. This makes the transition to work after graduation much easier.</p>


<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="studying-civil-engineering-at-ozyegin-university">Studying Civil Engineering at Ozyegin University</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="specialization-with-certificate-programs">Specialization with Certificate Programs</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University blends civil engineering not only with traditional methods but also with the technologies of the future. There are special certificate programs that offer students the opportunity to specialize in <strong>&#8220;Climate Change and Sustainability&#8221;</strong> or <strong>&#8220;Digitalization and Artificial Intelligence&#8221;</strong>. These certificates make a difference in job applications both locally and internationally.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="career-opportunities-in-turkey-and-abroad-after-graduation">Career Opportunities in Turkey and Abroad After Graduation</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As a civil engineer, you can work on major projects in Turkey, but you can also work in Europe or the Middle East. Özyeğin University graduates go into business life in consulting firms, public institutions, research centers or by establishing their own ventures.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition to being engineers, the Department of Civil Engineering equips students to be researchers, project managers or academicians.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="areas-where-graduates-can-go">Areas where graduates can go</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Building and construction companies (domestic/foreign)</li>



<li>Project consulting companies</li>



<li>Infrastructure and transportation projects</li>



<li>Academic career and research centers</li>



<li>Sustainable building and green energy projects</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="life-in-istanbul-ozyegin-campus-and-student-life">Life in Istanbul: Özyeğin Campus and Student Life</h3>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="cost-of-living-and-accommodation-for-international-students">Cost-of-living and Accommodation for International Students</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Living in a large and vibrant city like Istanbul provides international students with cultural diversity and social experience. Özyeğin University campus is located in an area close to the city center but surrounded by nature.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">University dormitories are very attractive for students with their safe and comfortable structure. In addition, the campus has a gymnasium, library, student clubs and many areas for social activities.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="location-and-social-facilities-of-the-campus">Location and Social Facilities of the Campus</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin&#8217;s campus stands out with its modern architecture in the east of Istanbul. Students can take nature walks between classes and spend time with their friends in social areas. In addition, the entrepreneurship center on campus provides students with support in project development.</p>


<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="you-can-be-the-civil-engineer-of-the-future">You Can Be the Civil Engineer of the Future!</h3>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="application-process-and-tips">Application Process and Tips</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are excited about Özyeğin University Civil Engineering, it is important to prepare for the application process in advance. It helps to research the necessary documents, English proficiency requirements and the visa process in advance. The university&#8217;s international office is very helpful in this regard.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>What documents should I upload when registering? </strong><br>Don&#8217;t worry, the university has made this process as transparent as possible for you. You can find a list of all required documents <a href="https://www.ozyegin.edu.tr/tr/ogrenci-hizmetleri/universiteye-kayitlar/yurt-disindan-ogrenci-ydo-kontenjanindan-kabul-alan-0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>. Uploading complete documents ensures fast processing of the application.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There is also good news for those planning to pursue a master&#8217;s degree: <br><strong>In engineering fields such as <strong>Industrial, Mechanical, Electrical-Electronics, Civil, Computer Engineering and Architecture</strong>, as well as programs with thesis such as <strong>Physics, Mathematics, Artificial Intelligence and Data Science</strong>, foreign students are exempt from the <strong>Graduate Education Entrance Exam</strong>. However, if you have exam results such as GRE, ALES, etc., presenting them can give you an additional advantage.</strong></p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-07-23T10:21:42Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:52:32Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ozyegin-university-civil-engineerin.webp","alt":"Foreign students conducting an experiment in the civil engineering laboratory at Ozyegin University campus.","title":"ozyegin-university-civil-engineerin"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'ozyegin-construction-engineering' );
