<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkey-scholarship-analysis-2025-an-overview">Turkey Scholarship Analysis 2025: An Overview</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As of 2025, the scholarship programs offered for foreign students in Turkey are quite diversified. Among these scholarships, the most preferred ones are <a href="https://ytb.gov.tr/daireler/uluslararasi-ogrenciler/turkiye-burslari" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YTB scholarships</a> and academic merit scholarships offered by universities themselves. Sports, arts and culture scholarships also open doors for students.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="state-supported-scholarships-or-foundation-scholarships">State Supported Scholarships or Foundation Scholarships?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">One of the most common questions is which type of scholarship is more advantageous. State-funded scholarships (e.g. YTB scholarships) are generally more comprehensive and offer additional benefits such as accommodation and health insurance. Foundation and private institution scholarships are generally based on merit or ability in a particular field.</p>


