<tr>
<td>Coverage</td>
<td>Education + Living Expenses</td>
<td>General Tuition</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Application Requirements</td>
<td>Broad (academic + social)</td>
<td>Mostly academic/art</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Facilities</td>
<td>Housing, health insurance</td>
<td>Some additional scholarships available</td>
</tr>
<tr>
