<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="recommendations">Recommendations</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is important to consider your academic, social and cultural interests when examining scholarship programs. While YTB scholarships stand out with their comprehensive support, university and foundation scholarships support more specific achievements.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="take-one-step-closer-to-your-dream-education">Take One Step Closer to Your Dream Education</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Now you know the results of the Turkey scholarship analysis and the best scholarship programs. Now it&#8217;s your turn! Take action now before you miss the application deadlines. Remember, the right scholarship program will positively affect both your education and social life. As the <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a> team, we are always with you to achieve your dream education.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-26T10:49:59Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:44:52Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/scholarship-options-for-foreign-students-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"A foreign student standing in front of a university building in Turkey","title":"scholarship-options-for-foreign-students-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'scholarship-analysis' );
