<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="documents-and-preparations-required-for-residence-permit-renewal">Documents and Preparations Required for Residence Permit Renewal</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In order to continue studying in Turkey as a student, you need to submit certain documents when applying for <strong>residency renewal</strong>. These documents are strictly controlled by the Immigration Authority. If you submit incomplete documents, your application may be delayed or rejected.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="application-forms-and-appointment-system">Application Forms and Appointment System</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The first step for the application is to fill out the residence permit renewal application form by logging into the e-residency system. After filling out the form, you can get an appointment date. It is very important to fill out the application form for renewal of residence permit in Turkey. Here are the key documents:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Passport (original and photocopy)</li>



<li>Existing residence permit card</li>



