</ol>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">By following these steps, you can submit a complete and strong application for a student visa to Turkey and minimize the risk of rejection. Remember, attention to detail will bring you one step closer to your dream!</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-21T06:17:57Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:45:21Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/conference-and-travel-scholarships-in-turkey-1.webp","alt":"Common mistakes in Turkey visa applications and how to fix them.","title":"conference-and-travel-scholarships-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'turkey-visa-applications-errors' );
