<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-the-department-of-artificial-intelligence-and-data-engineering">What is the Department of Artificial Intelligence and Data Engineering?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Artificial intelligence and data engineering is one of today&#8217;s most exciting and fast-growing fields. Özyeğin University Artificial Intelligence and Data Engineering Undergraduate Program aims to train engineers who design and develop the artificial intelligence systems of the future. In this department, students learn the basic principles of artificial intelligence, machine learning and data science applications and quickly adapt to developments in the sector.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-artificial-intelligence">What is Artificial Intelligence?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Artificial intelligence refers to technologies that enable machines to display human-like intelligence. This field aims to enable computers to mimic human skills such as learning, reasoning and problem solving. In particular, topics such as deep learning and natural language processing provide students with both theoretical and practical knowledge, enabling them to quickly enter the industry.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-data-engineering">What is Data Engineering?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Data engineering involves the processing, analysis and management of large amounts of data. In this field, students gain the technical skills necessary to make sense of data and make it applicable to the business world. At Özyeğin University, this program is supported by hands-on training using popular programming languages such as Python, C++ and Java.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-much-does-artificial-intelligence-and-data-engineering-education-cost-2025-2026">How Much Does Artificial Intelligence and Data Engineering Education Cost? 2025-2026</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Private universities in Turkey update their tuition fees every year. Özyeğin University has set the annual tuition fee for the Artificial Intelligence and Data Engineering program at <strong>22,000 USD</strong> for the 2025-2026 academic year. This fee is the standard list for students who do not receive any scholarship (i.e. 0% scholarship) and applies to the program for four years in English language.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more information about tuition fees and payment options, please visit <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-universitesi-egitim-ucretleri/" data-type="post" data-id="3013">Özyeğin University Tuition Fees and Payment Options</a>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In the table below, you can see the fee information and scholarship status of Özyeğin University Faculty of Engineering for 2025-2026:</p>


