<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="career-opportunities-after-graduation">Career Opportunities After Graduation</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are many job opportunities for students studying Artificial Intelligence and Data Engineering after graduation. Especially with the spread of artificial intelligence, employment opportunities in roles such as data scientist, machine learning engineer, artificial intelligence software developer and data analyst are quite wide.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="sectors-and-positions">Sectors and Positions</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Graduates can take part in the design and development of artificial intelligence-based systems in many sectors from banking to health, automotive to defense industry. Especially in R&amp;D and innovation centers, they can make a difference in the sector by contributing to the development of artificial intelligence-based products.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="where-do-graduates-work">Where Do Graduates Work?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ozyeğin University Artificial Intelligence and Data Engineering graduates can find jobs in technology companies in Europe and the United States as well as in Turkey. In particular, academic research and technology development centers, data analytics and artificial intelligence departments are among the primary targets for graduates of this department.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="advantages-of-studying-at-ozyegin-university">Advantages of Studying at Ozyegin University</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For foreign students, there are many advantages to choosing this department at Özyeğin University. The university stands out with its internationally recognized academic staff and modern laboratory infrastructure. Thanks to English education, students gain a competitive advantage on a global scale.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="academic-staff-and-research-opportunities">Academic Staff and Research Opportunities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The academic staff of the university consists of faculty members with international experience in artificial intelligence and data engineering. In addition, students can accelerate their academic development by participating in projects, competitions and international conferences.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="international-experience-and-language-education">International Experience and Language Education</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to the English language of instruction, students have the background to work not only in Turkey but also around the world. This situation provides a great advantage for foreign students both academically and socially.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="advantages-of-studying-in-turkey">Advantages of Studying in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey is an attractive destination for international students, both for its cultural richness and affordable cost of living. Özyeğin University campus is located close to the center of Istanbul, offering students the opportunity to participate in social and cultural activities.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="cultural-diversity-and-life">Cultural Diversity and Life</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey is located at the crossroads of Europe and Asia, making it a culturally rich country. Foreign students gain an unforgettable experience by experiencing the best examples of both East and West together.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="cost-and-scholarship-opportunities">Cost and Scholarship Opportunities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Education costs in Turkey are more affordable, especially when compared to European countries. In addition, Özyeğin University offers full and partial scholarships to international students, which significantly alleviate their educational expenses.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="haydi-be-the-engineer-of-the-future">Come on, Become the Engineer of the Future!</h2>


