<h3 class="wp-block-heading">5. Günlük yaşam için küçük elektronikler gerekli mi ve maliyeti ne kadar?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Laptop veya tablet, mini buzdolabı gibi küçük elektronikler faydalıdır; toplam maliyet yaklaşık 200–400 USD olabilir.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-07-31T14:40:18Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T19:23:36Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/list-of-essential-household-items-for-student-life-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"Essential household items for students living in Turkey","title":"list-of-essential-household-items-for-student-life-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'tr' AND "slug" = 'turkiyede-ogrenci-yasami-temel-ev-esyalari' );
